steps.name: Click to the icon to Edit/Delete/Download of the file name 'FileLessThan1MB.jpeg'
Upload the attachment with the file name is 'TxtFile.txt'
Input the value 'Quia velit qui molestiae.' to the Comment text box of the attachment
In the header 'Edit Attachment', click on the 'Save' button
Check whether the success pop up show
Get the description of the uploaded attachment in the field'File Name' with the value 'TxtFile.txt'
Get the description of the uploaded attachment in the field'Description' with the value 'Quia velit qui molestiae.'
Get the description of the uploaded attachment in the field'Date Added' with the value '2025-13-08'
